  "U_3: 10000x5000, S_3: 5000x5000, V_3: 5000x3": "",
  "The compact rank-3 SVD keeps 3 columns of U (10000x3), the 3x3 diagonal of singular values, and 3 columns of V (5000x3). Total storage: 30,000 + 9 + 15,000 = 45,009 vs 50,000,000.": "",
  "A numerical analyst finds that a 4x4 matrix A has singular values 100, 50, 0.01, and 0.005. What is the condition number, and what does it imply?": "",
