  "kappa = 2; the system is well-conditioned": "",
  "kappa = 0.00005; extremely well-conditioned": "",
  "kappa = 150.015; moderately conditioned": "",
  "kappa = sigma_max / sigma_min = 100 / 0.005 = 20,000. This large condition number means the system is ill-conditioned -- small perturbations in the data can cause large changes in the solution.": "",
  "A search engine uses SVD-based Latent Semantic Analysis (LSA) on a 10000-word x 50000-document term-document matrix. Keeping the top 300 singular values, what does each column of the reduced U_300 matrix represent?": "",
